one cucumber -- the fresher the better
seasoned rice vinegar like 1/2~ or so cup
like a tsp of salt 
like a few tbsp -> 1 cup of sugar. This is what makes it taste good

slice cucumber thinly
put in tupperware with rest of ingredients
after 30 minutes in fridge you can eat

i mostly eyeball the proportions youll gfigure out what you like after youmake it once
